# This document is intended to give steps through creating AWS-EC2 GPU powered instance request.

1. Click on the Support from the banner and choose support center.
2. New Page opens up, click on create case link.
3. New Page opens up, choose Service Limit Increase from *Regarding session.
4. Under limit type choose EC2 Instances
5. Under region section choose Ohio (you may need additional permissions for the other regions)
6. Primary Instance type choose p2.xlarge
7. Choose new limit value 15 (or any other your favorite number:)
8. Under contact method* choose your favorite contact method (preferably web if you don't want them to call you late in the night:)
9. Use case description: Write down how you want these instances to conduct deep learning experiments for your term project.
9. Click on submit. Done!